<inglise> IN ADDITION TO THE PLACES REFERRED TO IN PARAGRAPH 1, A TRANSPORT ALLOWANCE MAY ALSO BE GRANTED IN RESPECT OF PLACES WHERE THERE ARE NOT MORE THAN THREE OFFICIALS. </inglise>
<eesti> Lisaks l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud kohtadele v&otilde;ib transporditoetust anda ka kohtades, kus on kuni kolm ametnikku. </eesti>
<inglise> IN THIS CASE, THE COMMISSIONS SHALL NOTIFY THE COUNCILS AND THE LIST SUBMITTED SHALL BE DEEMED TO HAVE BEEN APPROVED IF WITHIN SIX WEEKS NO DELEGATION HAS EXPRESSED A WISH TO CONTEST THE GRANTING OF THE TRANSPORT ALLOWANCE IN RESPECT OF THOSE PLACES. </inglise>
<eesti> Sel juhul teatavad komisjonid n&otilde;ukogudele ja esitatud nimekiri loetakse heakskiidetuks, kui kuue n&auml;dala jooksul ei ole &uuml;kski delegatsioon avaldanud soovi vaidlustada transporditoetuse andmist nendes kohtades. </eesti>
<inglise> ARTICLE 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> TRANSPORT ALLOWANCES SHALL BE GRANTED ONLY TO OFFICIALS WHO: </inglise>
<eesti> Transporditoetust antakse &uuml;ksnes neile ametnikele, kellel: </eesti>
<inglise> - BECAUSE OF DIFFICULT HOUSING CONDITIONS IN THE PLACE OF EMPLOYMENT CANNOT OBTAIN APPROPRIATE ACCOMODATION ON PAYMENT OF A MONTHLY RENT WHICH, EXCLUDING, WHERE APPROPRIATE, THE COST OF UTILITIES SUCH AS HEATING, WATER, GAS, ELECTRICITY AND MAINTENANCE SERVICES, AMOUNTS TO LESS THAN: </inglise>
<eesti> - raskete elamistingimuste t&otilde;ttu t&ouml;&ouml;tamiskohas pole v&otilde;imalik saada kohast elamispinda, makstes igakuist &uuml;&uuml;ri, mis ilma selliste kommunaalteenuste hinnata nagu k&uuml;te, vesi, gaas, elekter ja hooldus, kui see on asjakohane, on v&auml;iksem kui: </eesti>
<inglise> 18 % FOR OFFICIALS UP TO AND INCLUDING GRADE B2, </inglise>
<eesti> kuni B2 astme (kaasa arvatud) ametnike puhul 18%, </eesti>
<inglise> 20 % FOR OFFICIALS FROM GRADE B1 TO GRADE A4, </inglise>
<eesti> B1-A4 astme ametnike puhul 20%, </eesti>
<inglise> 22 % FOR OFFICIALS ABOVE GRADE A4, </inglise>
<eesti> A4 astmest k&otilde;rgema astme ametnike puhul 22% </eesti>
<inglise> OF THE TOTAL EMOLUMENTS AS DETERMINED BELOW, AND PAY RENT OF MORE THAN 10 % OF THE TOTAL EMOLUMENTS AS DETERMINED BELOW. </inglise>
<eesti> k&otilde;ikidest allpool kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud rahalistest tasudest ja kes maksavad &uuml;&uuml;ri rohkem kui 10% k&otilde;ikidest allpool kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud rahalistest tasudest. </eesti>
<inglise> TOTAL EMOLUMENTS SHALL COMPRISE BASIC SALARY PLUS EXPATRIATION ALLOWANCE AND HEAD OF HOUSEHOLD ALLOWANCE, LESS THE COMPULSORY DEDUCTIONS REFERRED TO IN ARTICLE 64 OF THE STAFF REGULATIONS AND COMMUNITY TAX. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;ik rahalised tasud koosnevad p&otilde;hipalgast pluss kodumaalt lahkumise toetus ja perekonnapea toetus, miinus personalieeskirjade artiklis 64 osutatud kohustuslikult kinnipeetavad summad ja &uuml;henduse maksud. </eesti>
<inglise> THE AMOUNT THUS OBTAINED SHALL BE ADJUSTED BY THE CORRECTIVE FACTOR APPLICABLE AT THE PLACE OF EMPLOYMENT OF THE OFFICIAL CONCERNED. </inglise>
<eesti> Selliselt saadud summat kohandatakse k&otilde;nealuse ametniku t&ouml;&ouml;tamiskohas kohaldatava paranduskoefitsiendiga. </eesti>
<inglise> NO ALLOWANCE SHALL BE GRANTED IN CASES WHERE IT IS POSSIBLE TO MAKE USE OF JOINT MEANS OF TRANSPORT, NOR WHERE A SERVICE CAR IS USED, NOR WHERE A STANDARD LOCAL TRAVEL ALLOWANCE IS GRANTED. </inglise>
<eesti> Toetust ei anta, kui on v&otilde;imalik kasutada &uuml;hiss&otilde;idukeid, kasutatakse ametiautot v&otilde;i antakse standardset kohalikku transporditoetust. </eesti>
<inglise> THE AMOUNT OF THE TRANSPORT ALLOWANCE SHALL BE: </inglise>
<eesti> Transporditoetuse summa on: </eesti>
<inglise> - BFRS 600 PER MONTH WHERE THE DISTANCE BETWEEN THE OFFICIAL'S PLACE OF RESIDENCE AND PLACE OF WORK IS NOT LESS THAN 20 KILOMETERS AND NOT MORE THAN 30 KILOMETERS; </inglise>
<eesti> - 600 Belgia franki kuus, kui ametniku elu- ja t&ouml;&ouml;koha vahelise vahemaa pikkus on v&auml;hemalt 20 km ja k&otilde;ige rohkem 30 km; </eesti>
<inglise> - BFRS 1000 PER MONTH WHERE THE DISTANCE BETWEEN THE OFFICIAL'S PLACE OF RESIDENCE AND PLACE OF WORK IS GREATER THAN 30 KILOMETERS. </inglise>
<eesti> - 1000 Belgia franki kuus, kui ametniku elu- ja t&ouml;&ouml;koha vahelise vahemaa pikkus on &uuml;le 30 km. </eesti>
<inglise> ARTICLE 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> THIS REGULATION SHALL ENTER INTO FORCE ON 1 JANUARY 1966. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 1. jaanuaril 1966. </eesti>
<inglise> THIS REGULATION SHALL BE BINDING IN ITS ENTIRETY AND DIRECTLY APPLICABLE IN ALL MEMBER STATES. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
